    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">召集你的朋友，化身可爱的水豚，在这款快节奏的多人派对乱斗游戏中一决高下！踩在对手头上，在时间结束前赚取积分，并在 4 种混乱的游戏模式中称霸排行榜。</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><u><strong>各类游戏模式</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">经典模式</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">标准模式下，和好友同场竞技！抢积分、互相攻击，直到最后一刻才见分晓！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326980/extras/72e0f7a653fe6315530ea3e64564b6e4.poster.avif?t=1771881743\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326980/extras/72e0f7a653fe6315530ea3e64564b6e4.webm?t=1771881743\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326980/extras/72e0f7a653fe6315530ea3e64564b6e4.mp4?t=1771881743\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>淘金热模式</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">赛道上始终只有 1 枚金币。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">抢到金币的玩家可获得 3 分！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326980/extras/fff2eed37d44463be494bb4674b072a2.poster.avif?t=1771881743\" width=778 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326980/extras/fff2eed37d44463be494bb4674b072a2.webm?t=1771881743\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326980/extras/fff2eed37d44463be494bb4674b072a2.mp4?t=1771881743\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">夺旗模式</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">尽量长时间占有旗帜，获取珍贵积分。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">每隔 2 秒，你将获得 1 分！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326980/extras/8be7fae8e767e549d6ac3d11ebefe149.poster.avif?t=1771881743\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326980/extras/8be7fae8e767e549d6ac3d11ebefe149.webm?t=1771881743\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326980/extras/8be7fae8e767e549d6ac3d11ebefe149.mp4?t=1771881743\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">地板是熔岩模式</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">规则很简单：一旦踩到熔岩，几秒后便会被淘汰。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">小心选择落脚点，每次失误都会扣 1 分！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326980/extras/79d4cbf32a98a2f5c342b8ca7b7dd824.poster.avif?t=1771881743\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326980/extras/79d4cbf32a98a2f5c342b8ca7b7dd824.webm?t=1771881743\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326980/extras/79d4cbf32a98a2f5c342b8ca7b7dd824.mp4?t=1771881743\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">化身可爱水豚，击败你的朋友们！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326980/extras/f2245016d3737233b1827614d8888292.poster.avif?t=1771881743\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326980/extras/f2245016d3737233b1827614d8888292.webm?t=1771881743\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326980/extras/f2245016d3737233b1827614d8888292.mp4?t=1771881743\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">加入我们的 Discord！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326980/extras/601bf138badc8bc87d2ddd2cde7857b5.avif?t=1771881743\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326980/extras_big/601bf138badc8bc87d2ddd2cde7857b5.webp?t=1771881743 width=1560 height=302 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
